<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport"/>
    <title>Forest</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DotGothic16&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.png">

    <style type="text/css">

    body {
      overflow-y: hidden;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(/images/rain_bg.jpg);
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      height: 100vh;
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }

        .rain-container {
        background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(/images/rain_bg.jpg);
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        /*margin: 2% 5% auto 5%;*/
        background-size: 100% 100%;
      }
 
      .rain {
        height: 100vh;
        width: 100vw;
        background: url(/images/rain.png);
        z-index: 2;       
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        animation: rain 0.4s linear infinite;
        position: fixed;
      }

      .rain-container:before {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        content: '';
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
        background: #ffffff8a;
        /* animation: lighting 4s linear infinite; */
        opacity: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      @keyframes rain {
        0% {
          background-position: 0% 0%;
        }
        100% {
          background-position: 5% 100%;
        }
      }


      /* @keyframes lighting {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        10% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        11% {
          opacity: 1;
        }
        14% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        20% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        21% {
          opacity: 1;
        }
        24% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        104% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
      } */

      
      .rain_sound {
        position: relative;
        padding-top: 1%;
        float: right;
        z-index: 3000;
        outline: none;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        margin-right: 5%;
      }

      .rain-sound:hover,.rain-sound:active,.rain-sound:focus {
        outline: none;
        border: none;
      }

      .rain-btn {
        border-radius: 2rem;
        margin-left: 5%;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem 0.5rem 1rem;
        font-family: 'DotGothic16', sans-serif;
        border: double;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        z-index: 200;
        margin-bottom: 2px;
        position: absolute;
        background-color: #ffffff3b;
      }

      .rain-btn:hover,.rain-btn:active,.rain-btn:focus {
        background-color: #ffffff8a !important;
        border-color: #000000;
        color: #000000;
        font-weight: 800;
        outline: none !important;
      }

      .story-styles {
        font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        font-style: italic;
        text-align:center;
        color:lightgray;
         position:absolute;  
        height: auto;
        width: auto;
        margin: 250px;
        font-size:x-large;
        background-color: transparent;
        z-index: 1001; 
         /* Starting position */
 -moz-transform:translateY(100%);
 -webkit-transform:translateY(100%);	
 transform:translateY(100%);
      }

      .story{
 /* Apply animation to this element */	
 -moz-animation: story 25s linear 1;
 -webkit-animation: story 25s linear 1;
 animation: story 25s linear 1;
      }

/* Move it (define the animation) */
@-moz-keyframes story {
 0%   { -moz-transform: translateY(100%); }
 100% { -moz-transform: translateY(-100%); }
}
@-webkit-keyframes story {
 0%   { -webkit-transform: translateY(100%); }
 100% { -webkit-transform: translateY(-100%); }
}
@keyframes story {
 0%   { 
 -moz-transform: translateY(100%); /* Browser bug fix */
 -webkit-transform: translateY(100%); /* Browser bug fix */
 transform: translateY(100%); 		
 }
 100% { 
 -moz-transform: translateY(-400%); /* Browser bug fix */
 -webkit-transform: translateY(-400%); /* Browser bug fix */
 transform: translateY(-400%); 
 }
}
.story:hover {
 -moz-animation-play-state: paused;
 -webkit-animation-play-state: paused;
 animation-play-state: paused;
 }

 .story-btn {
  position:absolute ;
  display: inline-block;
  z-index: 1002;
  left:220px;
  top: 8px;
  width: 120px;
  height: 40px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  background-color: #ffffff3b;
  border-color: #000000;
  cursor: pointer;
  border:double;
  color: black;
  font-family: 'DotGothic16', sans-serif;
  font-weight:600;
  outline: none;
}
.story-btn:hover,.rain-btn:active,.rain-btn:focus {
        background-color: #ffffff8a !important;
        border-color: #000000;
        color: #000000;
        font-weight: 800;
        outline: none !important;
        font-weight:600;
      }


@media screen and (max-width:700px)
 {
   .rain-btn {
     visibility: hidden;
   }

   .story-btn {
     display: block;
     margin-top: 20%;
   }

   .rain-container {
      background: none;
   }

   .story-styles {
     margin: 3%;
     font-size: 0.8rem;
     -moz-transform:translateY(140%);
      -webkit-transform:translateY(140%);	
      transform:translateY(140%);
   }

   .story{
 /* Apply animation to this element */	
 -moz-animation: story 10s linear 1;
 -webkit-animation: story 25s linear 1;
 animation: story 50s linear 1;
      }

 }


    </style>
    
  </head>
  <body>
            <button class="rain-btn" onclick="openFullscreen();">Go  Fullscreen</button>
              <audio controls loop autoplay class="rain_sound" >
                <source src="/sounds/rain_s.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
              </audio>
    <div class="rain-container" controls id="myvideo">
 
      <div class="rain">          
      </div>
      <button class="story-btn">Read a story</button>
      <div class="story-styles" id="storyId">
        The gentle spray that touches your face is refreshing, to say the least.
        <br> A break from your monotonous nine to five cycle 
        <br>and an escape into the wilderness-
        <br> the sudden plan was not a mistake after all.
        <br><br>Back here sitting in this simple habitat of the 
        <br>gypsies and munching on roasted peanuts,
        <br> you realize that life is so much simpler than it sometimes reveals itself to be. 
        <br><br>Just like the clearing of the forest where your hut has been set down on,
        <br> there is also a clearing in your own life.
        <br>And you get there the same way you got here, 
        <br>by following your instinct and the map.
        <br> Right through the woods, never past it.
        <br><br>The rain washing down all the dirt of the past
        <br> while you mourn the gone makes you feel 
        <br>lighter than you have been in a while.
        <br> Someday soon, you know, you will have moved on from what has held you back. 
        <br><br>As you follow the trail of your thoughts freely,
        <br> the hundreds of forest sounds all muffled together 
        <br>like a nightly jazz almost makes you wonder
        <br> why you would ever go back home.
        <br><br><br>‘But you know why’, your heart whispers.
      </div>
    </div>


    <script type="text/javascript">

        var elem = document.getElementById("myvideo");
        function openFullscreen() {
          if (elem.requestFullscreen) {
            elem.requestFullscreen();
          } else if (elem.webkitRequestFullscreen) { /* Safari */
            elem.webkitRequestFullscreen();
          } else if (elem.msRequestFullscreen) { /* IE11 */
            elem.msRequestFullscreen();
          }
        }
      </script>

